column5: Good Morning, got the boat outta storage on Wednesday for a nice troll on Lake O, went two for three ,ended up with a nice brownie and a sweet greaser.....even did my first good deed of the season, and towed a dude in who had stalled. Yup things were going good till I blew a brake line on the van while pulling the boat out, I guess Karma is not a sure thing. Nice morning on the water though....                                     Cheers!
Nice fish,  to bad about the brake line.
Brake Line vs a couple trout in the boat. So I'll ask,would you do the trade again? Some nice fish.
Nice and flat out there, looks like a fun day, nice fish too.  Is that boat a Sylvan Striker?
What goes around comes around. One day when you need some help put on the water it will be there for you. Nic job on the trout
It was nice out there that day, the weather man said it was supposed to be windy, I glad he was wrong. My boat is a Starcraft , Chris.
